- [ ] Open `http://localhost:10000/`
- [ ] Test Case 1: "The moon is made of green cheese."
    - [ ] Enter text
    - [ ] Click "Run"
    - [ ] Verify result
    - [ ] Check model used
- [ ] Test Case 2: "Preliminary data suggests that a newly discovered mineral in the Andes could potentially reverse aging, though researchers caution that further peer-reviewed studies are required."
